{"tid":780043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人係咪壓抑好大!?","createTime":"2018-08-15T01:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T01:31:26.000Z","uid":132174,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce105a6b9eac252bd93d5f2767639c6151a26ded","tid":780043,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T01:14:32.000Z","msg":"生活喺香港已經夠大壓力<br />\n<br />\n好多成年人仲要唔識搵正常途徑舒發<br />\n<br />\n有冇陣時覺得自己其實喺度等一個機會有人冒犯你 然後就可以大條道理屌9人?<br />\n<br />\n甚至腦入面已經諗好哂要講咩反擊人? <br />\n<br />\n你撞到我, 唔理有心無意, 即刻兇一兇你先<br />\n一上巴士, 即刻啤住個關愛座, 睇吓坐𠴱嗰係咪「合資格」<br />\n<br />\n有啲人係公司俾老細鬧完, 就搵自以為低級過自己嘅人發洩去攞優越感, 甚至鬧埋屋企人<br />\n<br />\n情況同學校嘅bullying 完全一樣, 只係主角變咗做一班「假成熟」嘅大人<br />\n<br />\n保留童真同幼稚係兩回事, 點解冇人想好似一個小朋友咁追求一啲簡單嘅快樂?"},{"pid":"d7fec159b8564df931110fd3c3b98fde9d42bb66","tid":780043,"uid":154054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T01:16:26.000Z","msg":"連登都一樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a83c2959c8dfc1d46c155c8fea6af26517e950e","tid":780043,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7fec159b8564df931110fd3c3b98fde9d42bb66","tid":780043,"uid":154054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T01:16:26.000Z","msg":"連登都一樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T01:21:18.000Z","msg":"失控到已經當所有人都係自己嘅敵人 日本台灣韓國都好 不停放大人哋嘅缺點 好似大家比緊賽咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f8805ed6efb894e05450c29836026ddf951cde","tid":780043,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T01:31:26.000Z","msg":"推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}